*pkgcore-0.9.3 (28 May 2016)

  28 May 2016; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> +pkgcore-0.9.3.ebuild,
  pkgcore-9999.ebuild:
  version bump to 0.9.3

  28 May 2016; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  toss pypi upstream metadata for the pkgcore suite

  Github is the canonical source, especially as long as pypi only
  supports their new, hash-based download urls. Pypi downloads exist
  mostly to aid people doing pip installs.

